summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Molduflex landing page. All UI functionality works perfectly, but SEO meta tags are not served in development mode.

seo_issues.issue: Custom SEO meta tags and JSON-LD structured data from index.html not served in development mode
seo_issues.impact: Page shows 'Emergent | Fullstack App' instead of 'Molduflex | Materiais de Construção e Acabamentos de Alto Padrão'
seo_issues.details: React development server not using custom public/index.html. Production build works correctly with all SEO tags.

accessibility_issues.issue: Missing DialogTitle and Description for screen reader accessibility
accessibility_issues.console_warning: DialogContent requires a DialogTitle for accessibility

passed_tests: Hero section loads with logo, headline, and CTA buttons
WhatsApp CTA buttons open correct WhatsApp link (wa.me/5511922903862)
Products section displays all 6 categories (Climatização, Cozinha, Revestimento, Banheiro, Tintas, Pedras)
Product cards are clickable and open WhatsApp
Gallery section displays images and lightbox works with navigation
Sobre section renders with stats (4 stat cards)
Footer displays contact info (email, phone, Instagram)
Floating WhatsApp button is visible and functional
WhatsApp URL generation uses correct number (5511922903862)
All interactive elements have proper data-testid attributes
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix SEO meta tags not being served in development mode. The custom index.html with SEO content exists but React dev server is not using it. Consider switching to production build or fixing dev server configuration. Also add DialogTitle to Gallery lightbox for accessibility.
